\c 133
\s Kunaka korudo pakati pehama
\d Rwiyo rworwendo; rwaDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Tarirai, kunaka kwazvo nokufadza kwazvo Kana hama dzichigara pamwechete norugare.
\v 2 Zvakafanana namafuta anokosha ari pamusoro, Anoyerera pandebvu, Idzo ndebvu dzaAroni; Anoburukira kusvikira pamipendero yenguvo dzake;
\v 3 Zvakafanana nedova reHerimoni, Rinoburukira pamakomo eZiyoni; nekuti ndipo Jehovha paakaraira kuropafadza kwake, Ndihwo upenyu husingaperi.
